10:36.510 --> 10:38.554
-[Allison] And if we don't?
-[gasps]

10:39.764 --> 10:42.266
[Marcus] Then we'll have to settle this
the old-fashioned way.

10:43.976 --> 10:46.562
Look, we just fought a literal army.

10:46.646 --> 10:49.440
Okay? This doesn't need to get ugly.

10:49.523 --> 10:52.526
Let's all just calm down, and let's talk.

10:52.610 --> 10:54.654
Psst. Ben-er-ino.

10:55.488 --> 10:58.699
You look so much better alive
than you do dead.

10:58.783 --> 10:59.825
Am I right?

10:59.909 --> 11:01.494
Except that haircut.

11:02.495 --> 11:04.747
-What the hell did you just say?
-Come on, come on.

11:04.830 --> 11:07.875
Stop with all the hostility,
Mr. Grumpy Pants.

11:08.542 --> 11:10.127
Oh wow. Nice scar.

11:10.670 --> 11:11.504
Muy macho.

11:11.587 --> 11:13.089
Shut your mouth!

11:13.172 --> 11:15.132
You shut your mouth
and just hug your brother--

11:16.175 --> 11:19.011
-[Klaus groans]
-Hey! What the hell?

11:19.095 --> 11:21.472
-You didn't have to do that!
-Oh, I'm pretty sure I did!

11:21.555 --> 11:22.973
-He did.
-[Marcus] Get back!

11:23.057 --> 11:24.975
-[Vanya] Luther, hey!
-Back off! [grunts]

11:27.853 --> 11:29.563
["No More Heroes"
by The Stranglers playing]

11:29.647 --> 11:30.564
Oh shit!

11:33.359 --> 11:35.486
Bad touch, Luther! Bad touch!

11:35.569 --> 11:36.570
Sorry.

11:40.032 --> 11:42.118
♪ Whatever happened to ♪

11:43.452 --> 11:44.912
♪ Leon Trotsky… ♪

11:44.995 --> 11:45.996
[Klaus babbles]

11:46.080 --> 11:48.374
All right. Peace and love, peace and love.
Here I come.

11:48.457 --> 11:50.042
[Klaus groans] Damn it.

11:50.126 --> 11:51.627
Come at me, litter box!

11:51.711 --> 11:53.337
[Christopher speaks]

11:53.421 --> 11:56.132
Hey! Listen,
I have amazing hair, all right?

11:56.215 --> 11:57.550
This was era-appropriate!

11:57.633 --> 11:59.510
[groans]

11:59.593 --> 12:00.594
That's all you got?

12:02.012 --> 12:04.014
♪ And Sancho Panza? ♪

12:05.933 --> 12:09.645
♪ Whatever happened to the heroes? ♪

12:12.940 --> 12:15.526
You're alive. That's… great.
Or possibly horrible.

12:15.609 --> 12:18.112
-I'm not really sure yet.
-Is that some kind of weird smack talk?

12:18.195 --> 12:20.281
It's more of
an existential problem, really, Ben.

12:20.364 --> 12:22.199
Awesome. Well, here's your next problem.

12:25.953 --> 12:28.748
You know, even though
you're a total asshat now…

12:30.791 --> 12:32.084
[Ben crashes]

12:32.168 --> 12:34.295
…it's nice to see you again, really.

12:35.713 --> 12:37.089
[Diego yells]

12:37.173 --> 12:38.632
[Christopher speaks]

12:38.716 --> 12:41.218
Who's your daddy? I'm your daddy!

12:41.302 --> 12:44.847
Who's… your… daddy?

12:44.930 --> 12:46.932
[Diego screams]

12:52.188 --> 12:54.732
[raven cawing]

12:55.900 --> 12:56.859
I don't wanna fight you!

13:00.154 --> 13:02.156
Aww! Did you wanna be best friends?

13:02.823 --> 13:04.200
[Vanya groans]

13:07.119 --> 13:08.871
You know, for a blind person,
you're not bad.

13:08.954 --> 13:10.247
Who says I'm blind, asshole?

13:10.331 --> 13:11.290
[cawing]

13:13.667 --> 13:15.711
[grunting]

13:22.718 --> 13:24.011
Should I step in and help?

13:24.094 --> 13:26.180
-Nah. She's making a point.
-[fighting grunts continue]

13:26.263 --> 13:27.181
Popcorn?

13:30.601 --> 13:31.936
[Vanya] My turn.

13:35.731 --> 13:38.025
[Vanya screams, grunts]

13:38.108 --> 13:39.652
Art snob, huh?

13:40.361 --> 13:41.987
[Diego grunts]

13:43.948 --> 13:45.491
[Klaus] See? We're hugging!

13:45.574 --> 13:47.076
This is progress!

13:48.577 --> 13:52.456
♪ Whatever happened to the heroes? ♪

13:54.041 --> 13:57.127
-[Allison grunts]
-♪ No more heroes any more ♪

13:57.211 --> 13:59.046
♪ No more heroes… ♪

13:59.129 --> 14:00.130
By the way,

14:00.714 --> 14:02.883
I heard a rumor you can't move.
[voice echoes]

14:05.511 --> 14:06.679
-Hit me.
-What?

14:06.762 --> 14:08.556
-Come on. Hit me in the face.
-Okay.

14:08.639 --> 14:09.557
Hit me!

14:13.853 --> 14:17.523
♪ Whatever happened to the heroes? ♪

14:17.606 --> 14:20.234
[bones crunching]

14:20.317 --> 14:24.321
♪ Whatever happened to the heroes? ♪

14:26.991 --> 14:28.158
[Allison groans]

14:28.242 --> 14:29.159
I bet that hurt, huh?

14:29.243 --> 14:32.037
-[gasps]
-♪ No more heroes any more ♪

14:32.997 --> 14:35.666
♪ No more heroes any more ♪

14:35.749 --> 14:36.750
Fast little guy.

14:37.334 --> 14:39.003
[Allison panting]

14:39.086 --> 14:39.920
Thanks.

14:40.004 --> 14:40.921
[Five] No problem.

14:41.005 --> 14:43.549
Hey, short pants. What's up?

14:44.884 --> 14:47.720
Go help the others. I'll handle this one.

14:47.803 --> 14:49.638
-Okay.
-What are you, their mascot?

14:51.640 --> 14:52.683
[Jayme groans]

14:52.766 --> 14:53.934
More like their ringer.

14:54.018 --> 14:55.394
[hisses]

14:55.477 --> 14:56.353
Ugh.

14:56.854 --> 14:58.397
Hey, gross, all right?

15:01.442 --> 15:02.568
The hell?

15:04.987 --> 15:08.449
[emotional string music playing]

15:16.040 --> 15:17.041
Delores?

15:17.666 --> 15:18.500
